conference#Conference_participant: The parent of the conference participant is the track workshop chair. The active conference participant is the parent of the conference contributor and the regular author. The conference participant is also the parent of the conference contributor.

conference#Active_conference_participant: The active conference participant is the parent of the conference contributor, the regular author and the contribution co author. The active conference participant is the child of the invited speaker and the conference participant is the parent of the passive conference participant.

conference#Passive_conference_participan: The child of a conference participant is the child of a registered applicant and a conference applicant. The conference applicant is the parent of the conference participant.

conference#Person: The parent of the conference contributor is the committee member, co chair and the conference applicant. The conference applicant is the registered applicant and the reviewer is the parent of the track workshop chair.

conference#Review_expertise: Review expertise is a child of Thing.

conference#Submitted_contribution: The submitted contribution is the child of the regular contribution and the reviewed contribution. The reviewed contribution is the parent of the poster and the camera ready contribution. The written contribution is equivalent to the conference contribution.

conference#Reviewer: The reviewer is a child of the person who is the parent of the committee member. The committee member is the parent of the organizer who is the child of the organization.

conference#Regular_author: The regular author is the parent of both the active conference participant and the contribution co author. He is the child of the conference contributor and the contribution 1st author.

conference#Conference_contributor: The parent of the conference contributor is the registered applicant. The registered applicant is the parent of the paid applicant and the late paid applicant. The conference contributor is the child of the invited speaker and the regular author. The contributor is also the parent of the conference contributor.

conference#Contribution_1th-author: The contribution 1st author is the child of the regular author and the conference contributor. The invited speaker is the parent of the active conference participant and the invited speaker is the invited speaker.

conference#Contribution_co-author: The contribution co author is the child of the regular author and the conference contributor who is the parent of an active conference participant.

conference#Conference_contribution: The conference contribution is the parent of the poster, the conference announcement and the conference document. The conference contribution is the parent of the invited talk and the conference contribution is the parent of the conference contribution. The written contribution is the parent of the regular contribution and the reviewed contribution is the equivalent of the accepted contribution.

conference#Co-chair: The co chair is the child of the committee member and the parent of the track workshop chair.

conference#Committee: The committee is the parent of the organizing committee, the program committee and the steering committee.

conference#Committee_member: The committee member is the parent of the organizer and the co chair. The committee member is also the parent of the chair and the track workshop chair. The committee member is the child of the organizer and the chair.

conference#Abstract: Extended abstract is a child of extended abstract which is equivalent to regular contribution.

conference#Extended_abstract: The extended abstract is equivalent to the regular contribution which is parented by the written contribution and the submitted contribution.

conference#Invited_speaker: The invited speaker is the parent of an active conference participant, a committee member and a regular author. The 1st author is also a child of the conference contributor.

conference#Information_for_participants: The conference document is the parent of the conference contribution, the presentation and the invited talk. The information for participants is provided by the conference document.

conference#Conference_document: The conference document is the parent of the call for paper, the conference announcement and the poster. It is also the parent of the information for participants and the conference contribution.

conference#Organization: The parent of the organizer is the parent of the chair and the committee member.

conference#Regular_contribution: The conference contribution is the parent of the written contribution which is the parent of the submitted contribution. The reviewed contribution is the parent of the reviewed contribution which is the equivalent of the rejected contribution. The extended abstract is the parent of the regular contribution which is equivalent to the paper.

conference#Poster: The poster is the parent of both the submitted contribution and the accepted contribution. The conference contribution is the parent of the invited talk and the written contribution is the parent of the paper.

conference#Written_contribution: The written contribution is the parent of the submitted contribution and the accepted contribution. It is also the parent of the extended abstract which is the same as the extended abstract. The conference contribution is the child of the conference document and the written contribution is the child of the poster.

conference#Conference_applicant: The conference applicant is a child of a person who is the parent of a conference contributor and an active conference participant. The registered applicant is the parent of a paid applicant which is equivalent to an early paid applicant.

conference#Camera_ready_contribution: The camera ready contribution is a child of the accepted contribution which is equivalent to the reviewed contribution. The written contribution is also a child of the regular contribution which is parented by the extended abstract.

conference#Accepted_contribution: The accepted contribution is the parent of the camera ready contribution and is equivalent to the reviewed contribution. The written contribution is the child of the conference contribution and the conference document.

conference#Program_committee: The program committee is equivalent to the steering committee.

conference#Organizing_committee: The organizing committee is a child of the committee which is equivalent to the steering committee.

conference#Steering_committee: The steering committee is equivalent to the committee which is the parent of the organizing committee.

conference#Conference_volume: The conference volume is a child of conference.

conference#Conference: The conference is the parent of the conference volume.

conference#Call_for_paper: The call for paper is a child of conference document which is the parent of review.

conference#Conference_announcement: The conference announcement is the child of the conference document which is the parent of the call for participation.

conference#Paper: The paper is the child of the regular contribution and the written contribution. The poster is the parent of the submitted contribution.

conference#Invited_talk: The conference contribution, which is the parent of the presentation, is equivalent to an invited talk.

conference#Conference_part: The conference part is the parent of the workshop and the tutorial.

conference#Presentation: The conference contribution is the child of the conference document and is the parent of the invited talk.

conference#Chair: The chair of the committee is the child of the committee member who is the parent of the organizer who is the child of Thing.

conference#Track: The track is the child of the conference part and the parent of the tutorial.

conference#Workshop: The workshop is the child of the conference part and the parent of the tutorial.

conference#Tutorial: The tutorial is child of the conference part and the parent of the workshop.

conference#Rejected_contribution: The rejected contribution is the child of the reviewed contribution which is equivalent to the accepted contribution and the parent of the camera ready contribution.

conference#Reviewed_contribution: The submitted contribution is the child of the written contribution and the reviewed contribution is the parent of the rejected contribution. The reviewed contribution is equivalent to the accepted contribution which is the parent of the camera ready contribution.

conference#Review: The conference document is the parent of the conference contribution which is equivalent to a written contribution. The review contribution is the parent of the submitted contribution which is equivalent to a rejected contribution.

conference#Late_paid_applicant: The late paid applicant is a child of the registered applicant and the conference applicant. The registered applicant is also a child of the paid applicant.

conference#Paid_applicant: The late paid applicant is the parent of the late paid applicant. The registered applicant is the child of the conference applicant and the parent of the conference participant.

conference#Early_paid_applicant: Early paid applicant is equivalent to paid applicant and late paid applicant.

conference#Organizer: The parent of a conference applicant is the registered applicant. The registered applicant is the parent of a paid applicant. The late paid applicant is also the parent of the conference applicant. The committee member is also a child of the organizer of the Thing.

conference#Call_for_participation: The conference document is the parent of the conference announcement and the call for participation.

conference#Registeered_applicant: The registered applicant is the parent of the paid applicant, which is equivalent to late paid applicant. The registered applicant is also the child of the conference applicant and the conference participant.

conference#Track-workshop_chair: The track workshop chair is child of the person who is the parent of the conference contributor. The regular author is also the parent of the contribution co author.

conference#Conference_www: conference www is the parent of conference announcement and conference document.

conference#Review_preference: The review preference is a child of Thing.
